s/pitch-yourself/)**.","Subject":{"InScheme":{"Id":"urn:eciu:note","Type":"ConceptScheme"},"PrefLabel":{"En":"ParticipantInformation"},"Id":"8e2ebd63-5467-4cca-b0dc-0b8533ec75e3","Type":"Concept"}}],"HasPart":null,"Id":"urn:eciu:learningActivitySpec:8e2ebd63-5467-4cca-b0dc-0b8533ec75e3","Type":"LearningActivitySpecification"},"BannerImage":null,"MoreInformation":[{"NoteLiteral":"","Subject":{"InScheme":{"Id":"urn:eciu:note","Type":"ConceptScheme"},"PrefLabel":{"En":"SourceIdentifier"},"Id":"8e2ebd63-5467-4cca-b0dc-0b8533ec75e3","Type":"Concept"}},{"NoteLiteral":"","Subject":{"InScheme":{"Id":"urn:eciu:note","Type":"ConceptScheme"},"PrefLabel":{"En":"SubTitle"},"Id":"8e2ebd63-5467-4cca-b0dc-0b8533ec75e3","Type":"Concept"}},{"NoteLiteral":"As a graduate student, pitching yourself in the hope to obtain a job opportunity can be very hard: lack of confidence can creep in, compromising the outcome of your efforts. This course will teach how to present yourself with confidence, providing you with the right tools to communicate effectively and go from frustration to pride in your job search.","Subject":{"InScheme":{"Id":"urn:eciu:note","Type":"ConceptScheme"},"PrefLabel":{"En":"Introduction"},"Id":"8e2ebd63-5467-4cca-b0dc-0b8533ec75e3","Type":"Concept"}},{"NoteLiteral":"True","Subject":{"InScheme":{"Id":"urn:eciu:note","Type":"ConceptScheme"},"PrefLabel":{"En":"GenerateMicroCredentials"},"Id":"8e2ebd63-5467-4cca-b0dc-0b8533ec75e3","Type":"Concept"}},{"NoteLiteral":"**To apply, please upload:**\n\n- your CV in English;\n- if available, the English language certification\n- a brief motivational letter (1.000 characters) OR a motivational video (max 40\u2019\u2019, preferably youtube link) where you explain WHY you are interested in THIS learning opportunity.\n- Transcript of records\n\nPlease identify your Applicant status:\n\n1-UniTrento PhD or Student\n\n\u00A02-ECIU student\n\n\u00A03-Erasmus\u002B or Bilateral agreement student (in Trento for the whole semester)\n\n4-Student enrolled in Erasmus\u002B (non ECIU) partner University, applying for a challenge or BIP-Blended Intensive Program in Trento\n\n5-Other (extra fees may apply)\n\nStatus 1, 2 and 3 applicants need to submit two applications (similar documents, same deadline on 25 September):\n\n[SOI Admission Apply](https://webapps.unitn.it/Apply/it/MyUnitn/Home/334102/serv-studenti/Sel_SoI_2024_1)\n\n[ECIU Admission application](https://engage.eciu.eu/browse?universityIds=c7bc8551-6a54-ed11-bba2-6045bd886566\u0026amp;learningOppStatuses=1)\n\nStatus 4 and 5 applicants only submit their application in the [SOI Admission Apply](https://webapps.unitn.it/Apply/it/MyUnitn/Home/334102/serv-studenti/Sel_SoI_2024_1)\n\n[Here](https://www.soi.unitn.it/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Applying_to_SOI_ECIU_activities.docx.pdf)you can find guidelines on the application process.","Subject":{"InScheme":{"Id":"urn:eciu:note","Type":"ConceptScheme"},"PrefLabel":{"En":"AdmissionProcessInformation"},"Id":"8e2ebd63-5467-4cca-b0dc-0b8533ec75e3","Type":"Concept"}},{"NoteLiteral":"False","Subject":{"InScheme":{"Id":"urn:eciu:note","Type":"ConceptScheme"},"PrefLabel":{"En":"SimplifiedAdmissionProcess"},"Id":"8e2ebd63-5467-4cca-b0dc-0b8533ec75e3","Type":"Concept"}},{"NoteLiteral":"2024-06-14","Subject":{"InScheme":{"Id":"urn:eciu:note","Type":"ConceptScheme"},"PrefLabel":{"En":"ApplicationPeriodStartDate"},"Id":"8e2ebd63-5467-4cca-b0dc-0b8533ec75e3","Type":"Concept"}},{"NoteLiteral":"100","Subject":{"InScheme":{"Id":"urn:eciu:note","Type":"ConceptScheme"},"PrefLabel":{"En":"MaximumNumberOfSeats"},"Id":"8e2ebd63-5467-4cca-b0dc-0b8533ec75e3","Type":"Concept"}},{"NoteLiteral":"False","Subject":{"InScheme":{"Id":"urn:eciu:note","Type":"ConceptScheme"},"PrefLabel":{"En":"ECIULMSENabled"},"Id":"8e2ebd63-5467-4cca-b0dc-0b8533ec75e3","Type":"Concept"}},{"NoteLiteral":"","Subject":{"InScheme":{"Id":"urn:eciu:note","Type":"ConceptScheme"},"PrefLabel":{"En":"LMSUrl"},"Id":"8e2ebd63-5467-4cca-b0dc-0b8533ec75e3","Type":"